name: The Ghan Adelaide to Darwin with Charles Darwin Sunset Dinner Cruise
description:
Setting off from Adelaide, you'll travel coast to coast through the fiery Red Centre, experiencing Australia at its dramatic best on this all-inclusive journey. After your first night onboard take in an outback sunrise in Marla before the train makes its way to Alice Springs where a half a day of Off Train Experiences await. Your third and final day includes more extraordinary experinces in Katherine before arriving into Darwin as early evening falls. Transfer to your accommodation (as booked by you) and enjoy the following day at leisure. Cap off your trip to remember by joining Darwin Harbour Cruises and lap up a sunset you're unlikely to forget. 
Please Note: Accommodation is not included
